"    Noninflammatory acne",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 396px; height: 280px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Numerous open comedones are present on the chin.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
